{"tid":2119581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「正視聽」連登仔係撐醫護嘅！請大家表態！","createTime":"2020-07-22T07:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T12:49:50.000Z","uid":113222,"like":131,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"a00977030ccc4dba07ec96c95bebef56d6a2ff4d","tid":2119581,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"警察加薪但醫護就凍薪，竟然有人出黎屌醫護，而唔係屌政府？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護一直守護香港人，特別係疫情期間，一直緊守崗位。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，醫護界係唯一一個界別，有大規模實名罷工，明知會被清算，都幫香港人爭取封關。<br />\n<br />\n多謝醫護！撐醫護！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e944c04254c632e31566a57c0a4de22cf66f7704","tid":2119581,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebb532c1f703d7745ccc13512375308e10e8540","tid":2119581,"uid":274435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:39:53.000Z","msg":"多謝醫護"},{"pid":"ffc98ff7b38c69cb5082f02514c66327fb44aaf2","tid":2119581,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"support <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f865226507164ab103ed0977a6313076db326c","tid":2119581,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:41:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8738ec34aeaa559869f361e5cc6a5e83222b7f8e","tid":2119581,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"73887339e8af7d4452f3a4a313b314573dd4eec3","tid":2119581,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:42:10.000Z","msg":"撐醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔要中國產護士<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><blockquote>舊聞binC<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n節錄2011年蘋果新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=50296190\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&h=5bcbe452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使海外回來的註冊護士考試及格率也不足四成，<span class=\"red\">內地者更低，更有人連考三次仍不及格</span><br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n立法會議員余若薇表示最近收到投訴，一名在內地有18年工作經驗的資深護士，來港後發現很難搵工，故到護管局查詢報考註冊試的情況，結果發現單是填寫申請表格也極複雜，「<span class=\"red\">連填份表都咁難</span>，佢哋連考試嘅機會都冇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">申請表都唔識填 點寫排版</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節錄2014 西方日報 不貼link<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">三次不合格 失重考資格</span><br />\n<br />\n在內地任職護士逾十年的陳女士來港後，以海外護士資歷申請報考香港護士管理局的登記護士執業試。該考試要求若考生三次不能通過執業試，包括筆試及實習試，除非得到特別許可，否則會失去重考資格。<br />\n<br />\n陳聲稱通過筆試後，卻在實習試的考核中遭不公平待遇。她指，實習試要求考生在一小時內完成兩至三項操作，如<span class=\"red\">洗傷口、包紮及攙扶病人</span>等，惟考室規則各有不同，考核前並無通知考生。「A考室畀你一個鐘內做晒所有操作；B考室就要求每個操作做三十分鐘，時間冇得累積」。她指，考室的<span class=\"red\">洗手盆過低</span>，亦令考生難以符合無菌洗手的要求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">三十分鐘一個都完成唔到 好意思投訴考試不公</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">簡單扶抱都唔掂</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">黎到香港只會幫倒忙 <br />\n多謝曬中國資深護士</span></span><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote></span>"},{"pid":"a1e5695c0a5cc6c4d95b71e436a47bc7c42b47fd","tid":2119581,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:42:19.000Z","msg":"醫護加油💪"},{"pid":"c126348fa293a314bd265d20b029c6891effe82b","tid":2119581,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"支持醫護"},{"pid":"2877a771183c0b85fb194a77b15e68c36d5bc175","tid":2119581,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"多謝良心醫護<br />\n香港好在有你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffb75bb1946e87fc92f4dc93639c24411ec7f83","tid":2119581,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:43:45.000Z","msg":"支持！感謝！我會繼續減少不必要嘅社交活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8bf78284a236b8480cf2108b49efc45372e373","tid":2119581,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"I love you <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1570fe6af81f4e37b4a649b73279bf4c560c68c9","tid":2119581,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:44:09.000Z","msg":"連登唔撐香港醫護的話<br />\n第時引入支國醫護醫你嗰陣唔好怨"},{"pid":"531aafb9007c869ff1567f10ec8f7b767edc99d7","tid":2119581,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"多謝醫護"},{"pid":"0a79f6e46cb20233a321c7e211346feb0e94be1b","tid":2119581,"uid":235853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20